* Project management *                -*-muse-*-


Mark has worked on over fifty successful software projects. He has
developed an understanding of what makes projects work and how they
fail. 

He is able to work with a software development team to produce
high quality software, that is delivered for the lowest cost, and
meets the business goals. 

The key is using techniques that make the team more agile and focus on
the most important priorities of the project.


